#. type: Title =
#: ./modules/reference/pages/schedule/recurring-actions.adoc:2
#, no-wrap
msgid "Recurring Actions"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ./modules/reference/pages/schedule/recurring-actions.adoc:5
msgid ""
"The menu:Schedule[Recurring Actions] section shows all recurring actions "
"that you have permissions for."
msgstr ""

#. type: Labeled list
#: ./modules/reference/pages/schedule/recurring-actions.adoc:6
#, no-wrap
msgid "Recurring Action Details"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ./modules/reference/pages/schedule/recurring-actions.adoc:10
msgid ""
"View the details about an action from the action list.  In the "
"[guimenu]``Actions`` column, click the btn:[Details] icon for the action you "
"are interested in."
msgstr ""

#. type: Labeled list
#: ./modules/reference/pages/schedule/recurring-actions.adoc:12
#, no-wrap
msgid "Disabling Recurring Actions"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ./modules/reference/pages/schedule/recurring-actions.adoc:18
msgid ""
"Disabling an action stops the action recurring, but does not delete it.  To "
"disable a recurring action toggle the [guimenu]``Active`` switch off.  "
"Enable them again by toggling the [guimenu]``Active`` switch on.  Disabled "
"recurring actions remain in the list, but are not executed."
msgstr ""

#. type: Labeled list
#: ./modules/reference/pages/schedule/recurring-actions.adoc:20
#, no-wrap
msgid "Edit Recurring Actions"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ./modules/reference/pages/schedule/recurring-actions.adoc:26
msgid ""
"Edit an existing recurring action.  In the [guimenu]``Actions`` column, "
"click the btn:[Edit] icon for the action you want to change.  On the "
"[guimenu]``Schedule Recurring Highstate`` page, the existing properties are "
"pre-filled.  Make your changes, and click btn:[Update Schedule]."
msgstr ""

#. type: Labeled list
#: ./modules/reference/pages/schedule/recurring-actions.adoc:28
#, no-wrap
msgid "Delete Recurring Actions"
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ./modules/reference/pages/schedule/recurring-actions.adoc:33
msgid ""
"Deleting an action permanently removes it.  To start using the action again, "
"you will need to create a new action.  In the [guimenu]``Actions`` column, "
"click the btn:[Delete] icon for the action you want to delete, and confirm "
"the deletion."
msgstr ""

#. type: Plain text
#: ./modules/reference/pages/schedule/recurring-actions.adoc:35
msgid ""
"For more information about recurring actions, see "
"xref:administration:actions.adoc[]."
msgstr ""
